OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Frain in the east through the evening,
OL,7,Fclearing east overnight. Otherwise dry
OL,8,Fwith increasing clear spells from the
OL,9,Fwest, allowing a frost to develop.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA cold start with some frost,
OL,12,Fand variable cloud in the east.
OL,13,FOtherwise a dry day with increasingly
OL,14,Fsunny spells, but feeling a bit cooler
OL,15,Fthan recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
